comments: Paschall (GSW) lowers his shoulder and initiates contact with Gallinari (OKC), who is moving alongside his path in a legal guarding position.
Bowman (GSW) wraps Gallinari (OKC) off ball.
Burks (GSW) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact to Paul's (OKC) arm on the rip-through move.
Paschall (GSW) and Gallinari (OKC) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Gallinari (OKC) is already in Bowman's (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Paschall (GSW) makes marginal contact with Paul (OKC) on the perimeter.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) dislodges Adams (OKC) from his legally obtained position during rebounding.
Paul (OKC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Robinson III (GSW).
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly steals the ball from Bowman (GSW).
Robinson III (GSW) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Schroder (OKC) and Burks (GSW) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Chriss (GSW) is already in Gallinari's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gallinari (OKC) briefly places his arm around Chriss (GSW) as they disengage from the pick but does not affect his FOM.
Adams (OKC) cleanly blocks Paschall's (GSW) jump shot attempt.  Any ensuing arm contact is considered incidental.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) legally contests Burks' (GSW) shot near the rim.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact to Burks' (GSW) off arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Chriss (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Chriss (GSW) engages with Adams (OKC) but does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Chriss (GSW) is already in GIlgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Ferguson (OKC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Burks (GSW).
Paul (OKC) places a hand on Poole (GSW) but immediately drops it.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly blocks Poole's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
